data.description:
SELLER OFFERING 5.25%  VETERAN  APPROVED ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE, a tastefully updated Modern Home on an Oversized Lot you will swear is new.  As you look at this home, you come to believe it was just built yesterday.  Even beneath the surface, it is like new with 3 new Lennox High Efficiency A/C Units, and new Appliances.  And it is hard to find a home with better Curb Appeal. 

With Mountain Views on multiple sides, with Natural Area Open Space Desert (no one can build on) behind and to the side of you, you have the ultimate at the end of a cul-de-sac. 
On the first floor we have an Owner's Suite, Extra-large Kitchen with new Stainless-Steel Appliances, Stone Slab Counters, Breakfast Bar, Gas Range, Cabinets Space galore, and a Walk-in Pantry, all with Wide Plank Wood Looking Flooring And then on the Second Floor we have 3 more Bedrooms, an adjacent Full bath, and exceptionally Large Loft for Second Floor Entertainment.  And you top this off with a Resort Like Backyard with a 9.5 Ft Deep Diving Pool & Spa, Twin Water-Falls, Built-in BBQ & Counter-Top, RV Parking with a Gate, and a 3-Car Garage.  And finally, I forgot to mention Schools are with-in walking distance!
